<emphasis id="FF3C711AE944DB80C1FEAEBBA9A71A3C" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="43">Stephanopis xiangzhouica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
sp. nov., female epigyne, holotype. 
<emphasis id="AE0E2BCCF8620D77B66F78010D93BD4F" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="43">A</emphasis>
