<subSubSection id="19F0962029166D7DEB1DBFB6F7DB9D22" pageId="0" pageNumber="43" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="F64A900EED8C08CF7A3F5995FFC5F3BA" pageId="0" pageNumber="43">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="FEBAE0796A07917BB61A850E7C17F985" pageId="0" pageNumber="43">
Known only from the type locality in Jiangxi Province of China (Fig. 
<figureCitation id="B9559A9E09E444664D45720668D2152C" captionStart="Figure 17" captionStartId="F17" captionText="Figure 17. The location of the Jinggang Mountain National Nature Reserve in China indicated by a large black dot." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1095.72829.figure17" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/672179" pageId="0" pageNumber="43">17</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
